            "body": "> What you want to archieve is called localization\n\nIt’s not, though it is (or at least can be) related (eg. in the `.desktop` file case I mentioned).\n\nI think you misunderstand/misread what this issue is asking for.\n\n> If Microsoft is so evil, […]\n\nOkay… ? I don’t see how this is of any relevance to this issue. If you wish to discuss my GitHub profile or my personal convictions, there’s contact information in my GitHub profile (as well as my e-mail being in most of my commits), so you should be able to figure out a way to contact me directly. Using an unrelated GitHub issue for this is… weird.",
